746
01:06:46,210 --> 01:06:48,044
I'm not gonna do it.

747
01:06:49,588 --> 01:06:51,548
How dare you?

748
01:06:54,260 --> 01:06:56,177
You tricked me.

749
01:06:56,679 --> 01:06:58,138
You--

750
01:06:58,305 --> 01:07:00,015
You came to that meadow...

751
01:07:00,182 --> 01:07:04,394
